{"tid":1565234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個週末-中秋集會-參觀天水圍-銅鑼灣行街","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:26:32.000Z","uid":252031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53cd5ede1fe6108f35b97d9b74e61b073fad0045","tid":1565234,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"連登呢排好明顯有人帶風向互屌，屌前線，屌和理非，屌榮光，屌唱歌，希望大家兄弟爬山，各有各做，大家位置唔同，可以幫手嘅都唔同，各自努力，呢排文宣真係唔夠，求下大家幫手吹雞<br />\n今晚各區有集會慶祝中秋<br />\n仲有獅子山之路<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fL5SVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fL5SVy.png&h=40adab7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDDWe8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDDWe8X.jpg&h=b147ce6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8PFmrfG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8PFmrfG.jpg&h=7e38767b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JF3nU89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJF3nU89.jpg&h=ea1be99e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日有參觀天水圍嘅活動啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tz3OQHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTz3OQHJ.jpg&h=4674716d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有915主線 銅鑼灣shopping<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5p37mPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5p37mPL.jpg&h=8aa041fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住機場搞手取消咗機場交通壓力測試，唔好去錯地方參觀啊<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e731795afd79f281f4a3c3167aecea7b31a0ab","tid":1565234,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=6e7ea6d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"8721722b85c205cdcb28641794166a8b40419052","tid":1565234,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://